text: Mario Casas Sierra (born 12 July, 1986, A Coruña) is a Spanish actor. He has starred in Los hombres de Paco (2007–2010), Fuga de cerebros (2009), and Tres metros sobre el cielo (2010) == Other websites == Category:Spanish actors Category:Galician people Category:1986 births Category:Living people
